// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3137 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 84201095-94b1-5f27-b0cd-cc963429762d

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*")
